category.message:

When there is only initial sources, the number of time bins or the length of time bins must obligatory be specified
for the default value of the length of time bins (average time between two successive Poisson source events)
is not available.


 The option used for the LEAR keyword does not exist.
 The LEAR options take an integer as its parameter:
@ 0: no learning;
@ 1: learning the geometry;
@ 2: learning the neighbourhood;
@ 3: recovery of a learning file.


The library has not been defined using the $C2$ keyword for the nuclide $C1$.
This keyword must be placed either:
- before the definition of the material compositions;
- before the definition of the nuclides for the considered material composition;
- or after the nuclide names.


The data format has not been defined using the $C2$ keyword for the nuclide $C1$.
This keyword must be placed either:
- before the definition of the material compositions;
- before the definition of the nuclides for the considered material composition;
- or after the nuclide names.


The temperature (K) has not been defined using the $C2$ keyword for the nuclide $C1$.
This keyword must be placed either:
- before the definition of the material compositions;
- before the definition of the nuclides for the considered material composition;
- or after the nuclide names.
